trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support in a visual designer for the <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for utforming i en visuelle utformeren for den <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.Design.DynamicDataManagerDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.Design.DynamicDataManagerDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Generates the HTML markup that is used to render the associated <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager"></xref> control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Genererer HTML-koden som brukes til å gjengi den tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager"> </xref> kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The GetDesignTimeHtml method calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.CreatePlaceHolderDesignTimeHtml%2A> method to generate a simple rectangular placeholder representation that displays the type and ID of the control.
trans-unit.target: Metodekall GetDesignTimeHtml den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.CreatePlaceHolderDesignTimeHtml%2A>metode for å generere en enkel rektangulær plassholder representasjon som viser type og IDen for kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.CreatePlaceHolderDesignTimeHtml%2A>

trans-unit.source: The HTML markup that is used to render the associated <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager"></xref> control at design time.
trans-unit.target: HTML-koden som brukes til å gjengi den tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager"> </xref> kontrollen under utformingen.
